legacy.full_text:
Don’t know if it’s just me but any Everton optimism has been sucked out of me over the past week.
The squad looks horribly stale and thin, we’ve no money to remediate, no owners and a very one-dimensional way of playing.

Sorry to be negative but this place is a sounding board.
